Package: python-nosedjango
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python-django, python-nose (>= 0.10.0)
Description: A nose plugin for Django unit tests
 This is a Nose unit test framework for Django unit tests.
 .
 Nosedjango handles creating and removing test databases before every
 single test keeping the tests isolated. It also has experimental
 transaction support to speed up unit tests.
